  "title": "Sales Operations Executive #73766",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturer of Polymeric Materials</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Sales Operations Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Kallang</li><li>Working Hours: Mon-Fri: 8am – 5.30pm</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic salary $2,800 - $3,800 + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Develop new business development leads with existing and new customers</li><li>Attend to Sales enquiries, generation of quotation</li><li>Follow up quotation, Monitoring samples & Shipments schedules</li><li>Work closely with Operation, Engineering & Quality teams to offer the best solutions for customers</li><li>Ensuring proper records of sales-related documents (quotation, customer enquiries and other relevant documents)</li><li>Any other related sales duties assigned by management</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum ‘O’ level or equivalent</li><li>Proficient in MS Office applications</li><li>Bilingual in English & Mandarin (able to communicate effectively with our Chinese business associates)</li><li>Excellent communication, interpersonal & organizational skills with forward-thinking attitude</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#73766 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
